    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation de libxml2 Python2 module</title>



      <!-- Editors note: Use \-\-root= instead of DESTDIR= when updating. -->
<para>
        Pour construire le module <application>Python 2</application>, lancez&nbsp;:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>cd python             &amp;&amp;
python2 setup.py build</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        Pour installer le module <application>Python 2</application>, en tant
qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> lancez&nbsp;:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>python2 setup.py install --optimize=1</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

